-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ryw1665702822019_2.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ryw1665702822019_2.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ryw1665702822019_2.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ryw1665702822019\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Replace Contiguous Spaces\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify whether all contiguous spaces in the field should be replaced by a single space.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ryw1665702822019__section_w2843ab1b5b1_w2844ab1b5_w2845ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ryw1665702822019__table_d869e1_d870e1_d871e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ryw1665702822019__table_d869e1_d870e1_d871e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ryw1665702822019__table_d869e1_d870e1_d871e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ryw1665702822019__table_d869e1_d870e1_d871e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ryw1665702822019__table_d869e1_d870e1_d871e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Sets the <code class=\"ph codeph\">RCS</code> field syntax code, so contiguous spaces are\n                           replaced by a single space.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ryw1665702822019__table_d869e1_d870e1_d871e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ryw1665702822019__table_d869e1_d870e1_d871e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Spaces are left unchanged in the field.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ryw1665702822019__section_eky_fpq_qwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d514495e124\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ryw1665702822019__p_d99089e1_d99090e1_d99091e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zlt1665702557043.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zlt1665702557043.html\" title=\"The Field Syntax property specifies the input format for data, including the entry format (for example, 1-Dec-14 or 20141201), the allowed characters, and whether the field is mandatory or read-only.\">Field Syntax</a>\n</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8422569\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8422569\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content